# HumanAIOS document-control ownership.
# Enforce via branch protection → "Require review from Code Owners".
# NOTE: these @humanaios-ui/* groups are GitHub TEAMS that must be created for
# enforcement; until then GitHub treats unknown owners as no-op (safe default).

# The control system itself — owned by the control maintainer (mesh-support)
/document-registry.yaml     @humanaios-ui/doc-control
/CONTROLLED_DOCUMENTS.md    @humanaios-ui/doc-control
/.doc-control/              @humanaios-ui/doc-control
/.github/workflows/document-control.yml   @humanaios-ui/doc-control

# Area owners (align with HAIOS-<AREA>-* doc_id prefixes)
/GOVERNANCE.md              @humanaios-ui/governance
/REGISTERED.md              @humanaios-ui/research

# Default: any other controlled markdown routes to the control maintainer
*.md                        @humanaios-ui/doc-control
